                    <event
                        ana="http://syriaca.org/keyword/council-of-chalcedon-451 http://syriaca.org/keyword/exile http://syriaca.org/keyword/persecution http://syriaca.org/keyword/monasteries http://syriaca.org/keyword/monks http://syriaca.org/keyword/wandering">
