                            <persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/1813">John</persName> was expelled from <placeName ref="http://syriaca.org/place/87">Gaza</placeName>, 
                            and traveled into <placeName ref="http://syriaca.org/place/2734">Alexandria</placeName>, finally settling in the 
                            <placeName ref="http://syriaca.org/place/473">Ennaton</placeName>. </desc>
                    </event>
                </listEvent>
                <bibl type="primary">
